{"tid":1519760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望前線手足想好方法避免重演上星期荃灣","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T18:04:43.000Z","uid":156878,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8800deb0b4805cafed8ab8b366d8309b751925d","tid":1519760,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"上星期荃灣很多手足被捕. 速龍突擊好多人走唔切被捕.<br />\n<br />\n有人話係因為中後排企得太密導致退路搗塞. 跑得唔快既都要注意企位.<br />\n<br />\n還要注意深水埗好似尋晚警察躲後荒巷突擊等.<br />\n<br />\n作為和理非真係好唔想見到大家受傷或被捕.<br />\n<br />\n總之大家Be Water.<br />\n<br />\n我們既援軍暫看9月初美國國會復會. 大家要保留實力. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a15e6455e32b3eecee9cad5f68f677304c661a","tid":1519760,"uid":108225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"大家一定要諗清楚後果 <br />\n人哋部署好 走就得<br />\n<br />\n留喺度對峙 等到大圍捕<br />\n告暴動嘅話 之後幾年嘅生活都係要自己過<br />\n<br />\n唔想任何手足冇咗自由<br />\n請大家三思<br />\n<br />\n不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a927771446ee6a1fa8d24c265e1fcd7b630f2166","tid":1519760,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a15e6455e32b3eecee9cad5f68f677304c661a","tid":1519760,"uid":108225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"大家一定要諗清楚後果 <br />\n人哋部署好 走就得<br />\n<br />\n留喺度對峙 等到大圍捕<br />\n告暴動嘅話 之後幾年嘅生活都係要自己過<br />\n<br />\n唔想任何手足冇咗自由<br />\n請大家三思<br />\n<br />\n不被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"每個手足都很重要."},{"pid":"594f2d6d342bfe1317d9531fec7fa67caad9fe38","tid":1519760,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c